105
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:46,000
We had that narrative and kind of drive to make it formless and with our conventional rigging that we can do that.

106
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:49,000
We were doing prototyping before the feature even kicked off.

107
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:52,000
Like we were already meeting with animation and tech art to say,

108
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:57,000
